429
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,820
Pôjdeme?

430
00:29:39,820 --> 00:29:41,050
Čo? Kam?

431
00:29:41,890 --> 00:29:45,950
Neznášam ťa! Ty si zabudla?

432
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:48,530
Dnes...

433
00:29:48,530 --> 00:29:51,970
mi dajú dole sadru.

434
00:29:51,970 --> 00:29:53,630
Oh, to je pravda!

435
00:29:53,630 --> 00:29:54,740
Rýchlo poďme.

436
00:29:54,740 --> 00:29:57,310
Poďme ju dať dole a niečo dobré si zajesť.

437
00:29:57,310 --> 00:29:57,990
Ah!

438
00:29:57,990 --> 00:29:59,380
Poďme.

439
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:03,360
Budem ťa podopierať.

440
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:03,970
Ďakujem.

441
00:30:03,970 --> 00:30:07,640
- Opri sa o mňa.
- Áno.

442
00:30:08,610 --> 00:30:13,870
Prepáč, že som zabudla.

443
00:30:24,530 --> 00:30:25,540
Tak ako?

444
00:30:25,540 --> 00:30:27,250
Si v poriadku?

445
00:30:27,250 --> 00:30:29,160
Hej. Je to osviežujúce.

446
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,990
Myslím, že teraz už môžem konečne žiť.

